episodes.title: How Thailand’s Darkest Cult got Exposed
episodes.description:
In this video, we explore one of Thailand’s darkest and most disturbing cults — led by Thawee Nanra, a self-proclaimed holy man whose followers believed his urine and phlegm could cure disease.
